fields.notes:
Halfling Luck: For every point of luck expended gain +2 to his roll. Luck recovers similar to HP. Luck can be burned and applied to allies rolls.

Horn of Kings;
Thrice [1] per week, drinking from the horn grants +4 to a Fort save against poisons; thrice per month [2], drinking from the horn heals the drinker 1d12 hp/level; once, and only once, drinking from the horn grants the imbiber a DC 10 Fort save to return from death. When this final power is used, the horn shatters, losing all its powers forever.
